                    &lt;img alt=&quot;下午察：柯洁卷入棋盘外的风波&quot; title=&quot;下午察：柯洁卷入棋盘外的风波&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/6f507cd84c311596c253732d767faff3646934956ffd4d52f1afaad6f30462c6&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
